sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant S as Supabase Auth
    participant G as Google OAuth
    participant DB as Database

    U->>F: Click Login Button
    F->>S: signInWithOAuth(google)
    S->>G: Redirect to Google
    G->>U: Show Google Login
    U->>G: Enter Credentials
    G->>S: Return OAuth Token
    S->>S: Create/Update User
    S->>F: Return Session
    F->>DB: Fetch User Profile
    DB->>F: Return Profile Data
    F->>U: Show Logged In State
